  Open Microscopy Environment - Install Notes (Java Client - Mac OS X)
  --------------------------------------------------------------------


  Install Procedure
  _________________

  Extract the downloaded bundle in any directory on your local file system.
  After doing this, your directory should contain:

    * The "OMERO.insight" application.
    * This install file.



  Running The Software
  ____________________

  Double-click one of the application icons within the installation
  directory. A splash screen will pop up. Enter your OMERO user name, password
  and the name of the server then press the log in button.
  You should not have to modify the port value.
  Enjoy OMERO!